body: Could of at least made her do it with Momon

Granted, we ARE seeing an incomplete sample of the larger work, but still... The only way this could possibly occur with her character is if she was ordered to do it by Momon/Ainz. And even then, that would be an absurd stretch to make, given HIS character isn't really like that, either.
No, I'm with Null on this, there is a limit to how much you can stretch the characters before they basically are completely different characters with the same face.
